squad.Brief.takeaways | hasValue | One additional candidate shape for the demo activity, in the same format as m1dgley's menu. Mechanic-shape: 'fix a real broken thing in front of the judge.' Adds the steady-hand-operator axis that wasn't on the four-shape menu. Pairs naturally with Shape A; could replace Shape C if Rob wants a higher-signal cheap option. Decision is still Rob's per law #5.
